name: NOTHING TO LOSE
description:
The last part of the series "Tumbuh dan berkembang".

Adolescence is a phase where we do many things for the first time. Whether it's learning to play music, falling in love and heartbreak for the first time, learning to smoke for the first time and other stupid things.

Without realizing it, our good and bad in adolescence have shaped our personality today, from the process we have gone through making us more ready to face challenge after challenge, and making us better prepared for the next process.

In the end, by looking back at the recorded memory, we can learn to go through the difficult times we are currently facing, because if we remember we were at the lowest point of life and were able to get through it. now is the time to try again to keep growing and developing, until the time that forces us to fall.
